reviews.text: Very good price, and the quality is better than it's price

If you are not a Chinese you may suffer from the crowd and it looks pretty old, not very clean. The waiters are just as rude like every other place in Hong Kong. She may not remember the cost of your meal. So you have to remember that. The food however is pretty ok and in comparison, cheaper than other place in the neighbor.

Local, neighbourhood congee shop that is great value for money.
Congee comes piping hot and rice rolls are made to order.  Great for a quick meal.
Traditional. No MSG

The place was crowded, but we could find the seat relatively quickly. The ladies working there were actually quiet patient with us, not rude, not rushing, did not look frustrated. The congee rice porridge was surprisingly well seasoned, I was expecting it to be more bland as it usually is. The baked bread and fried soy buns were also rather good. Soy milk was so-so though, don't expect much from it.

result.name: 永明粥店

reviews.text:
好，吃了兩次粥。

粥底做了特別處理，很好吃，肉料是大塊呈現的方式，材質新鮮。
油條也不錯，一份粥有17和23港幣兩類，風格有別廣州一帶。

我很喜歡，下次路過香港會前往。
每當想食粥就會想到它，那種最尋常的街坊小店。
地方雖舊，但香港傳統美食，價錢實惠，腸粉連花生醬鼓油好味
Very good price, and the quality is better than it's price
什麼粥都有鱼，猪，牛肉再加上不同味道的正。😋😋你地都可以過來嘗試下。👍
